{
  "texts": [
    "This area will be worth investigating further especially using robotics for activity and motion detection.",
    "There is a tiny proportion of documents grouped in this category.",
    "The documents are focused on using the TM for image annotation (Luo et al. 2011), image segmentation (Feng and Jiang 2011), and image classification (Zhang et al. 2020).",
    "For example, in the case of image annotation, the caption words given to the image and its accompanying document are used to label the image.",
    "Alternatively, the co-occurrence of visual features and the words can be captured to label the image."
  ]
}